Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:37.24,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Until I die, no end in sight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.00,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I believe in our bond
